# Test Search API Endpoints
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tool

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/manage
Content-Type: application/json

### Basic Search Test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=test&page=1&page_size=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Advanced Search Test
POST http://localhost:3000/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "document",
  "filters": {
    "file_type": ["pdf", "doc"],
    "department": ["Engineering"]
  },
  "search_type": "basic",
  "highlight": true,
  "pagination": {
    "from": 0,
    "size": 20
  }
}

### Search Suggestions Test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/suggestions?q=doc
Content-Type: application/json

